{"tid":1041014,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"勁量逆天之作，摺疊屏幕+10000mAh+5G 網絡，最緊要夠平!!!","createTime":"2019-02-28T13:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T07:52:47.000Z","uid":50534,"like":9,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"338358866aa0569c111da232b43993771ae57698","tid":1041014,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/02/28/energizer-power-max-p8100s/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F02%2F28%2Fenergizer-power-max-p8100s%2F&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=f663e78c\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/02/28/energizer-power-max-p8100s/</a><br />\n勁量逆天之作，摺疊屏幕+10000mAh+5G 網絡，最緊要夠平!!!<br />\nBy Marco - 二月 28, 2019<br />\n在昨天，Energizer(勁量) 憑藉一款厚達1.8cm，配備 18000mAh容量電池和採用升降式前置雙鏡的「大嚿」手機 Power Max P18K Pop 吸引了不少消費者關注。除了這一款超長待機的磚頭手機，還給我們展示了旗下的摺疊屏幕手機。<br />\n<br />\n勁量 Power Max P18K Pop，18000mAh 電池的驚人手機<br />\n<br />\n在 MWC 2019 會場上 Energizer 推出的摺疊屏幕手機型號為 Power Max P8100S，結合以往的情況，我們從「Power Max」的命名可以了解到該手機的電池容量肯定不低，現實也是如此，達到了10000mAh，一躍成為了摺疊屏幕手機中的行動電源(主編按：你確定不是行動電源中的摺疊屏幕手機?)！<br />\n<br />\n在外型設計上，Power Max P8100S 採用與 Samsung Galaxy Fold 一樣的摺疊方案，為內外雙屏，內摺疊。外屏為6吋，內屏展開為8.1吋。<br />\n<br />\n性能規格方面，Power Max P8100S 搭載了 Snapdragon 855 處理器，配以 8GB RAM+256GB ROM。拍攝上，前置2400萬像素自拍鏡頭和後置4800萬+1200萬像素雙鏡，支援 PDAF，還會有支援 5G網絡的手機版本。<br />\n<br />\n外觀上，在目前的推出的摺疊屏幕手機中，該手機的鉸鏈應該是最不好看的，可能與大容量的電池有關係。如果對於美觀方面沒有太高要求的話，Power Max P8100S 是你可以考慮入手的摺疊屏幕手機，因為有著旗艦配置，大容量電池和 5G 的它，售價卻是最便宜的，為850歐元（約HK$7620 或 NT$29900），會於2019年11月上市<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/2332433423243.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F2332433423243.jpg&h=c6abf9fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/24324332324432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F24324332324432.jpg&h=69925258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/4323433433324423-1280x720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F4323433433324423-1280x720.jpg&h=8940b6d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62ba822da4e730ad4029944b04fc61ba3d7ce5ef","tid":1041014,"uid":22553,"like":79,"dislike":5,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:41:57.000Z","msg":"中間摺痕，火車咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b1240c4a90e6543a1b05e5e7ee31a900585dc4","tid":1041014,"uid":113335,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:42:38.000Z","msg":"好撚柒 成部手風琴咁"},{"pid":"81689d1c5675f0129555ec34a8a1b7791bceed0b","tid":1041014,"uid":61675,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"62ba822da4e730ad4029944b04fc61ba3d7ce5ef","tid":1041014,"uid":22553,"like":79,"dislike":5,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:41:57.000Z","msg":"中間摺痕，火車咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:43:11.000Z","msg":"地鐵果條野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfaae9d1bfc4bd8a9508c783b187c740ca709842","tid":1041014,"uid":36134,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:45:40.000Z","msg":"屌 你做返電池算啦"},{"pid":"c4e7b17b3f2fc1bb6e2c8b098526bfdfba9d6512","tid":1041014,"uid":8042,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:51:57.000Z","msg":"摺芒嗰邊冇實物圖？"},{"pid":"88bf27eff1668183a39c22cd94b9f810471bf3a5","tid":1041014,"uid":71620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"部磚頭機點拎出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁大舊"},{"pid":"1d6ae8747bf07a555c3b9f7637ec0217b3f71311","tid":1041014,"uid":219081,"like":28,"dislike":4,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T15:34:01.000Z","msg":"1年段 iPhone 